ptions</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#AB5959;--shiki-dark:#CB7676\">?</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\">: </span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#2E8F82;--shiki-dark:#5DA994\">ThemeOptions</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\">):</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#2E8F82;--shiki-dark:#5DA994\"> Theme</span></code></span></template></v-menu></span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\">(&#123;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"--shiki-light:#A0ADA0;--shiki-dark:#758575DD\">    // 在这里定义自己的主题配置文件路径</span></span>\n<span class=\"line diff add\"><span style=\"--shiki-light:#998418;--shiki-dark:#B8A965\">    </span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#998418;--shiki-dark:#B8A965\"><v-menu class=\"twoslash-hover\" popper-class=\"shiki twoslash-floating vp-copy-ignore vp-code\" theme=\"twoslash\"><span>configFile</span><template v-slot:popper=\"&#123;}\"><span class=\"twoslash-popup-container vp-copy-ignore\" v-pre=\"\"><code class=\"twoslash-popup-code\"><span style=\"--shiki-light:#B07D48;--shiki-dark:#BD976A\">ThemeFeatureOptions</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\">.</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#B07D48;--shiki-dark:#BD976A\">configFile</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#AB5959;--shiki-dark:#CB7676\">?:</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#B07D48;--shiki-dark:#BD976A\"> string</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#AB5959;--shiki-dark:#CB7676\"> |</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#AB5959;--shiki-dark:#CB7676\"> undefined</span></code><div class=\"twoslash-popup-docs vp-doc\" vp-content=\"\"><p>自定义主题配置文件路径</p></div></span></template></v-menu></span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\">: </span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#B07D48;--shiki-dark:#BD976A\"><v-menu class=\"twoslash-hover\" popper-class=\"shiki twoslash-floating vp-copy-ignore vp-code\" theme=\"twoslash\"><span>path</span><template v-slot:popper=\"&#123;}\"><span class=\"twoslash-popup-container vp-copy-ignore\" v-pre=\"\"><code class=\"twoslash-popup-code\"><span style=\"--shiki-light:#AB5959;--shiki-dark:#CB7676\">const </span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#B07D48;--shiki-dark:#BD976A\">path</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\">: </span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#2E8F82;--shiki-dark:#5DA994\">path</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\">.</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#2E8F82;--shiki-dark:#5DA994\">PlatformPath</span></code></span></template></v-menu></span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\">.</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#59873A;--shiki-dark:#80A665\"><v-menu class=\"twoslash-hover\" popper-class=\"shiki twoslash-floating vp-copy-ignore vp-code\" theme=\"twoslash\"><span>join</span><template v-slot:popper=\"&#123;}\"><span class=\"twoslash-popup-container vp-copy-ignore\" v-pre=\"\"><code class=\"twoslash-popup-code\"><span style=\"--shiki-light:#B07D48;--shiki-dark:#BD976A\">path</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\">.</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#B07D48;--shiki-dark:#BD976A\">PlatformPath</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\">.</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#59873A;--shiki-dark:#80A665\">join</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\">(...</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#B07D48;--shiki-dark:#BD976A\">paths</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#393A34;--shiki-dark:#DBD7CAEE\">: </span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#B07D48;--shiki-dark:#BD976A\">string</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\">[])</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#393A34;--shiki-dark:#DBD7CAEE\">: </span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#B07D48;--shiki-dark:#BD976A\">string</span></code><div class=\"twoslash-popup-docs vp-doc\" vp-content=\"\"><p>Join all arguments together and normalize the resulting path.</p></div><div class=\"twoslash-popup-docs twoslash-popup-docs-tags vp-doc\" vp-content=\"\"><span class=\"twoslash-popup-docs-tag\"><span class=\"twoslash-popup-docs-tag-name\">@param</span><span class=\"twoslash-popup-docs-tag-value\"><code>paths</code>  paths to join.</span></span><span class=\"twoslash-popup-docs-tag\"><span class=\"twoslash-popup-docs-tag-name\">@throws</span><span class=\"twoslash-popup-docs-tag-value\">&#123;TypeError} if any of the path segments is not a string.</span></span></div></span></template></v-menu></span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\">(</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#B07D48;--shiki-dark:#BD976A\"><v-menu class=\"twoslash-hover\" popper-class=\"shiki twoslash-floating vp-copy-ignore vp-code\" theme=\"twoslash\"><span>__dirname</span><template v-slot:popper=\"&#123;}\"><span class=\"twoslash-popup-container vp-copy-ignore\" v-pre=\"\"><code class=\"twoslash-popup-code\"><span style=\"--shiki-light:#AB5959;--shiki-dark:#CB7676\">var </span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#B07D48;--shiki-dark:#BD976A\">__dirname</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\">: </span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#2E8F82;--shiki-dark:#5DA994\">string</span></code><div class=\"twoslash-popup-docs vp-doc\" vp-content=\"\"><p>The directory name of the current module. This is the same as the\n<code>path.dirname()</code> of the <code>__filename</code>.</p></div><div class=\"twoslash-popup-docs twoslash-popup-docs-tags vp-doc\" vp-content=\"\"><span class=\"twoslash-popup-docs-tag\"><span class=\"twoslash-popup-docs-tag-name\">@since</span><span class=\"twoslash-popup-docs-tag-value\">v0.1.27</span></span></div></span></template></v-menu></span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\">, </span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#B5695977;--shiki-dark:#C98A7D77\">'</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#B56959;--shiki-dark:#C98A7D\">custom/config.ts</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#B5695977;--shiki-dark:#C98A7D77\">'</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\">), </span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"--shiki-light:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\">  }),</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"--shiki-light:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\">})</span></span></code></pre>\n</div></div><div class=\"hint-container warning\">\n<p class=\"hint-container-title\">如果你是新手用户，不推荐自定义配置文件路径，这可能带来意想不到的问题。</p>\n</div>\n<h2 id=\"页面配置\" tabindex=\"-1\"><a class=\"header-anchor\" href=\"#页面配置\"><span>页面配置</span></a></h2>\n<p>使用在页面的顶部使用 YAML 语法的 Frontmatter，可以为每个页面进行单独配置主题。</p>\n<div class=\"code-block-title\"><div class=\"code-block-title-bar\"><span class=\"title\"><VPIcon name=\"vscode-icons:file-type-markdown\"/>article.md</span></div><div class=\"language-md\" data-highlighter=\"shiki\" data-ext=\"md\" style=\"--shiki-light:#393a34;--shiki-dark:#dbd7caee;--shiki-light-bg:#ffffff;--shiki-dark-bg:#121212\"><pre class=\"shiki shiki-themes vitesse-light vitesse-dark vp-code\" v-pre=\"\"><code><span class=\"line highlighted\"><span style=\"--shiki-light:#005CC5;--shiki-light-font-weight:bold;--shiki-dark:#79B8FF;--shiki-dark-font-weight:bold\">---</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"--shiki-light:#393A34;--shiki-dark:#DBD7CAEE\">title: 文章标题</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"--shiki-light:#393A34;--shiki-dark:#DBD7CAEE\">createTime: 2024/09/08 22:53:34</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"--shiki-light:#393A34;--shiki-dark:#DBD7CAEE\">permalink: /article/xxx/</span></span>\n<span class=\"line highlighted\"><span style=\"--shiki-light:#1C6B48;--shiki-light-font-weight:bold;--shiki-dark:#4D9375;--shiki-dark-font-weight:bold\">---</span></span></code></pre>\n</div></div><p>在 Markdown 文件的顶部，使用 <code v-pre>---</code> 分隔符，在两个 <code v-pre>---</code> 之间的部分被称为 Frontmatter。\n这部分通过 <code v-pre>YAML</code> 语法进行配置。</p>\n<div class=\"hint-container tip\">\n<p class=\"hint-container-title\">如果你不了解 <code v-pre>YAML</code>，可以通过 <RouteLink to=\"/article/ecxnxxd0/\">这篇博客</RouteLink> 了解它的基本用法。</p>\n</div>\n","env":{"base":"/","filePath":"/Users/zhangfan/zfan2356/github/AI-Router/ai-router-v2/docs/notes/theme/config/intro.md","filePathRelative":"notes/theme/config/intro.md","frontmatter":{"title":"配置说明","createTime":"2024/03/02 10:48:14","permalink":"/config/intro/"},"sfcBlocks":{"template":{"type":"template","content":"<template><h2 id=\"概述\" tabindex=\"-1\"><a class=\"header-anchor\" href=\"#概述\"><span>概述</span></a></h2>\n<p><mark>vuepress-theme-plume</mark> 是基于 <a href=\"https://v2.vuepress.vuejs.org/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">VuePress</a> 的主题。\n因此，配置需要遵循 VuePress 的配置规范。</p>\n<p><strong>在 VuePress 中，有三种配置类型:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>站点配置</strong>: 这是你在 配置文件 <em>（如 <code v-pre>.vuepress/config.ts</code>）</em> 中直接导出的对象</li>\n<li><strong>主题配置</strong>: 传递给 <code v-pre>plumeTheme()</code> 的对象参数</li>\n<li><strong>页面配置</strong>: 由在页面顶部基于 YAML 语法的 Frontmatter 提供</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"vuepress-配置文件\" tabindex=\"-1\"><a class=\"header-anchor\" href=\"#vuepress-配置文件\"><span>VuePress 配置文件</span></a></h2>\n<p>VuePress 站点的基本配置文件是 <code v-pre>.vuepress/config.js</code> ，但也同样支持 TypeScript 配置文件。\n你可以使用 <code v-pre>.vuepress/config.ts</code> 来得到更好的类型提示。</p>\n<p>具体而言，VuePress 对于配置文件的路径有着约定（按照优先顺序）：</p>\n<p>当前工作目录 <code v-pre>cwd</code> 下：</p>\n<ul>\n<li><code v-pre>vuepress.config.ts</code></li>\n<li><code v-pre>vuepress.config.js</code></li>\n<li><code v-pre>vuepress.config.mjs</code></li>\n</ul>\n<p>源文件目录 <code v-pre>sourceDir</code> 下：</p>\n<ul>\n<li><code v-pre>.vuepress/config.ts</code> <Badge type=\"tip\" text=\"推荐使用\" /></li>\n<li><code v-pre>.vuepress/config.js</code></li>\n<li><code v-pre>.vuepress/config.mjs</code></li>\n</ul>\n<p>基础配置文件示例：</p>\n<div class=\"code-block-title\"><div class=\"code-block-title-bar\"><span class=\"title\"><VPIcon name=\"vscode-icons:file-type-typescript\"/>.vuepress/config.ts</span></div><div class=\"language-ts\" data-highlighter=\"shiki\" data-ext=\"ts\" style=\"--shiki-light:#393a34;--shiki-dark:#dbd7caee;--shiki-